      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZIPPING GRYLLIS (4) goes very well this trip starting 25 times for 14 wins and five minors. Missed the frame latest (20.97) when sixth over 365m at this track in a Mix 1/2/3. Looks well placed and should feature. CUMBRIA RICH (5) jumped from this box and scrambled home to a narrow Grade 5 win at this track over 365m latest (21.23). Harder here but expected to measure up. NICKO QUEEN (2) racing well without winning, placing at her last four runs. Last time finished 2nd over 365m at this track beaten 8 lengths (21.31) behind Born Little in a Grade 4/5 on January 22. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and four minor placings to her credit. Will give a great sight again. NICKO KING (7) has won at this course and distance, cannot be ruled out.",
